Bitstream name: ibm_dp_intra_422.m2v
Decoded files name: ibm_dp_intra_422.decoded[1-66].[yuv]

This bit stream tests a decoder's ability to handle
high bandwidth compressed data and motion comp data.
The "high bandwidth" P frames contain a random mix of
intra macro blocks and dual' macro blocks.  The intra
macroblocks use 12275 bits of compressed data.  The dual'
blocks use half pel interpolation to increase bandwidth
requirements.  Each high bandwidth P frame uses a little less
than tne vbv buffer size bits.  Note that the intra blocks
are made up of synthetic data, and will be light green to black.

Picture size:    720x512
Frame rate:      29.970000
Chroma:          4:2:2
Bit rate:        50000000
vbv buffer size: 9437184
Dc precision:    11-bits
Pic structure:   Frame
No Frames:      66

Frame
0      I frame
1      High bandwidth P frame
2      P frame
3      P frame
4      P frame
5      P frame
6      P frame
7      High bandwidth P frame
8      P frame
9      P frame
10     P frame
11     P frame
12     P frame
13     High bandwidth P frame
14     P frame
15     P frame
:       :
:       :


The format of the reconstructed frames is:

	4:2:2 frame ("display" order) 8 bit samples per compenent.

	width  = 720
	height = 512


                   <--------width--------->
                  +------------------------+
                  |                        |      ^
                  |                        |      |
                  |                        |      |
                  |                        |      |
                  |     Luminance Pels     |    height
                  |                        |      |
                  |                        |      |
                  |                        |      V
                  +-----------+------------+
                  |           |      ^
                  |           |      |
                  |           |      |
                  |  Cb pels  |    height
                  |           |      |
                  |           |      |
                  |           |      V
                  +-----------+      -
                  |           |      ^
                  |           |      |
                  |           |      |
                  |  Cr pels  |    height
                  |           |      |
                  |           |      |
                  |           |      V
                  +-----------+      -
                   <-width/2->





